<p style="text-align: left;">Spirit of Play mysteriously came into being in the middle of 2008, after a long period of idle talk and ineffectual body language. Like snowflakes, no two SOP songs are the same, and many are quite different even from themselves. The perceived members of the group are: Wendy Texas (electric 12-string and voice), Tom Woolfenden (drums), stephenmcaines (bass and voice) and Will Eaves (hair of the dog and voice). Their credentials are dubious.</p>
